  "embedding_text": "Golden Sojourn Resort Tunchang - khách sạn 2.0 sao tại Đồn Xương.\nĐịa chỉ: Yanglifang Block, Jianwen Rd, Đồn Xương, Đồn Xương, Trung Quốc.\nThe Golden Sojourn Resort Tunchang provides a great place for travelers to relax after a busy day. The Golden Sojourn Resort Tunchang offers a pleasant stay in Tunchang for those traveling for business or leisure. \nQionghai Railway Station and Bo Ao Airport are located 56km and 85km away respectively. With multiple attractions nearby including Tunchang Library, Wuzhi Shan Hongdoupo Bailu Amusement Park and Tunchangxian Museum, guests will find plenty to keep themselves occupied. \nAfter a long day of sightseeing, guests can retire to the comfort of the hotel. This Tunchang hotel offers parking on site.\nCác loại phòng: Deluxe Standard Double Room Suite; Basic Room - Double Occupancy (Double bed) (Basic Room - Double Occupancy (Double Bed)); Basic Standard Double Room.\nGần: Qionghai Bo'ao Airport, Sân bay Quốc tế Mỹ Lan Hải Khẩu, Sân bay Quốc tế Phượng Hoàng Tam Á.",
